# Routing Guidelines

## Blog Route Structure
- `/`: Home page with featured/recent posts
- `/posts`: Blog post listing page
- `/posts/[slug]`: Individual blog post pages
- `/categories/[category]`: Category-specific post listings
- `/tags/[tag]`: Tag-specific post listings
- `/about`: About page
- `/search`: Search functionality

## Route Implementation
- Use dynamic routes for blog posts
- Implement pagination for post listings
- Create reusable layouts for consistent blog structure
- Handle metadata for SEO optimization
- Implement proper loading states for content

## Navigation
- Use Qwik's Link component for internal navigation
- Implement breadcrumb navigation for better UX
- Add category and tag navigation
- Include search functionality
- Ensure proper meta tags for blog SEO